scrape_and_unpack_ble

Source: R/FrankenFIM_scrape_and_unpack_ble.R
FrankenFIM_scrape_and_unpack_ble.Rd

wrapper around BLE handles

Usage

FrankenFIM_scrape_and_unpack_ble(
  database_path = NULL,
  HUCID = NULL,
  quiet = TRUE,
  overwrite = FALSE,
  full = FALSE
)

Arguments

database_path

PARAM_DESCRIPTION, Default: NULL

HUCID

PARAM_DESCRIPTION, Default: NULL

quiet

PARAM_DESCRIPTION, Default: TRUE

overwrite

PARAM_DESCRIPTION, Default: FALSE

full

PARAM_DESCRIPTION, Default: FALSE

Value

unzipped dir of BLE data

Details

Hitting https://webapps.usgs.gov/infrm/estBFE/ and https://www.arcgis.com/apps/dashboards/1e98f1e511fc40d3b08790a4251a64ee
